Package: hex2ascii
Version: 2.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, tesseract-ocr, python3-pyside6, python3-pil, python3-numpy, python3-pytesseract
Maintainer: djOB2EOTWQW1 <noreply@example.com>
Description: Decode hex strings from images via Tesseract OCR
 Hex2ASCII reads an image of a hexadecimal string and decodes it to ASCII text.
